<div class="salecs-add">
  <form nz-form [formGroup]="SaleForm">
    <nz-form-item>
      <nz-form-label [nzSpan]="4"><span style="padding-left: 10px;">手机号：</span></nz-form-label>
      <nz-form-control [nzSpan]="7" class="reuse_chk">
        <input type="text" nz-input class="com_input" formControlName="salecsPhone" placeholder="用于接收APP端产品咨询消息"
          [(ngModel)]="salecsPhone" maxlength="32" />
          <nz-form-explain *ngIf="SaleForm.get('salecsPhone').dirty && SaleForm.get('salecsPhone').errors">
            <ng-container *ngIf="SaleForm.get('salecsPhone').hasError('required')">
                必填选项
            </ng-container>
            <ng-container *ngIf="SaleForm.get('salecsPhone').hasError('phone')">
                输入手机号码格式不正确
            </ng-container>
        </nz-form-explain>
      </nz-form-control>

    </nz-form-item>

    <div nz-col [nzSpan]="4" class="salecs-add-label"><span>关注马克巴微信公众号：</span> </div>
    <div nz-col [nzSpan]="18" class="salecs-add-info" style="margin-bottom: 52px;">
      <img src="https://qiniu.madrock.com.cn/qr/gzh.jpg" alt="">
      <span>
        请确保用以上手机号注册的微信账号，扫码关注马克巴公众号，关注后可接收在线装修客户咨询消息
      </span>
    </div>

    <div nz-col [nzSpan]="4" class="salecs-add-label"><span>绑定在线装修小程序：</span></div>
    <div nz-col [nzSpan]="18" class="salecs-add-info">
      <img src="https://qiniu.madrock.com.cn/qr/xcx.jpg" alt="">
      <span>
        请确保用以上手机号注册的微信账号，扫码绑定在线装修小程序，绑定后才能接收到马克巴公众号的消息推送
      </span>
    </div>

  </form>
</div>
<div class="about">
  提交前请确保已经用以上手机号 关注了马克巴公众号 和 绑定了在线装修小程序
</div>
<div class="btn">
  <button nz-button nzType="default" (click)="back()">返回</button>
  <button nz-button nzType="primary" (click)="submit()">提交</button>
</div>